Menu Structure
--------------

* Single Player
* LIVE Multiplayer
  - Create Match
  - Join Match
* Awardments
* Help & Options
  - How to Play
  - Controls
    + A to select then move/attack
    + B to cancel selection
    + X to place a piece
    + Start to open menu
  - Options
    + Music on/off
    + Sound on/off
    + Change storage device
  - Credits
* Get Full Version
* Exit to Dashboard


